Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}「初次見面！梅老師」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}{\an8}{\fs24}{\c&H295072&}山吹高中  入學考試會場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃好不容易才爬起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽都替你著急了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  轉換好心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  媽媽  我去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  冷靜點好好加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「孤注一擲」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上午  筆試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離考試開始還有15分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿好準考證
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鉛筆盒  鉛筆盒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記普通的文具了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鉛筆還算好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橡皮只有素描橡皮泥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「欲速則不達」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  現在才來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試要開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在走廊上跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要摔了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野屋老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼重要的日子居然遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底搞什麼飛機呀  那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試結束  請放下鉛筆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「吾生也有涯，而知也無涯」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入學考試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年會進來幾個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是全部住滿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我校學生一直承蒙你的關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年會有怎樣的孩子住進來  我都很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話  請收下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不勝感激
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午  專業課考試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,題目是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子上的瓶子自由放置  用鉛筆表現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要畫墊在下面的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要表現出掉在布上的花瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓶子？布？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「求人不如求己」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:06:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都要比我畫得好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要集中精力考試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  考試結束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放下鉛筆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「謀事在人，成事在天」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  雖然也有不怎麼樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已經竭盡全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  來接我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  難道你一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「明天又是嶄新的一天」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美裡前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是入學考試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英  起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2月14日  合格發表前一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  不快點喝就要冷掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是情人節吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要送巧克力給爸爸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始就只說「嗯」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃真是個小笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是  媽媽  明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「否極泰來」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻嘿咻嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2月15日  合格發表
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面真熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  沙英？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英也起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋  你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿成那樣不冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是合格發表的日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在露出笑容的人將會成為我們的後輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子落榜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭得那麼傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「玉不琢，不成器；人不學，不知道」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸媽媽  我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}4月5日  由乃的搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有忘記東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心身體哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好地做飯吃哦  還有還有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係的  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過於擔心了  那麼我真的走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs24}再見啦  我出發了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃真的能一個人生活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs24}爸爸媽媽  我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃已經15歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住的地方也是學校的宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已經去看過很多次了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs24}我走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs24}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}由乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「杞人憂天」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs30}{\c&000&}{\bord0}向陽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李搬到哪裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去開門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我的房間是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,２０１  ２０１
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬場的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的房間裡有美裡……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是之前住的人留下的名牌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「金窩銀窩不如自己的草窩」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的鄰居嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搬了在搬了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是住在隔壁的宮子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕎麥面還沒有好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}註：日本人搬家時有給鄰居吃蕎麥面的習俗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}註：蕎麥和旁邊的發音一樣  意思是「到你的旁邊來了」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家蕎麥面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}食慾滿滿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美術科一年級的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我沒有想到會合格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都還沒有做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮子學姐  今後請多多指教…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  我沒有說重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃烏冬面的時候  拜託你用關西湯料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏東面？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「寧要實惠，不要恭維」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我從春天開始也是一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣是美術科
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到這裡才一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同是初學者  多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說是３月初就搬過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}再次是2月10日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我早就盯上這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  請多指教  宮子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我小宮就好了  或者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就請叫我由乃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小由乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用加「小」了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃比
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃衛  由乃助  由乃Ａ夢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃吉  由乃丈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  由由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你知道向陽莊的基礎知識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向陽莊基礎知識之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立山吹高中  因為有美術專業班
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各個地區到來的入學志願者也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一所非常受歡迎的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向陽莊基礎知識之二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向陽莊是位於山吹高中正前方的小公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向陽莊基礎知識之三
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聚集了美術科的怪人們而聞名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,400)}{\bord0}怪人→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這實在是太沒有禮貌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(170,400,270,400)}{\bord0}怪人→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,400)}{\bord0}怪人→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一個  我真不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又忘記說一件重要的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想還在施工  現在都沒有水出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:14:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從剛才開始就有用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還做了蕎麥面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道只有我家裡不出水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  不過也許是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想著沒有水  前天的洗澡水都用掉的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮  水費付了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「三個臭皮匠，賽過諸葛亮」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由的正樓下的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美術科二年級弘學姐的家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩嗎  我好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋學姐  在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮  從上面的房間傳來靈異聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(193,140)}{\c&H386C8F&}{\bord0}怪人２
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是今天搬到樓上的由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs24}{\c&H386C8F&}{\bord0}對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃也是美術科的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家來畫畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也兼作自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子什麼的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家就來畫兔子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋學姐  有沒有油性粗馬克筆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是有  不過畫的是兔子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「世上無難事，只怕有心人」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋學姐畫得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我畫的是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也畫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是畫得非常好？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀樹大草原的動物們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  越發看不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁的沙英也是美術科的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一樣  現在是二年級
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在做寫小說的工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:17:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  小說的截稿日就是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說已經第４天熬夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就直接回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係  等下會拿晚飯去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集了美術科的怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(575,270)}{\c&H6F6F6F&}{\bord0}怪人３
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近的事情會再告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如買東西和平時去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你們知道附近有澡堂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有去過那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連一次澡堂都沒有去過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天好像是休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙…騙你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋學姐  為什麼要撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧走吧  洗澡洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  只有今天我實在不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以問你為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想留到明天吃的  還是忍不住…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近有家很好吃的蛋糕店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人的話  就沒有人來阻止了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  就是這個問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我的話  我就能幫你吃掉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能幫助 尋學姐減肥  又能填飽我的肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不勞而獲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為你那句話用錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小宮才開始獨自生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是頑強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡的日子也很早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3月5日  宮子的搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還因為自己能不能做好而擔心不已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有什麼厲害的  馬上就習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由也會這樣的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮  你到底要吃還是要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話題轉回來  小宮為什麼會想要來這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入學考試結束後回家時  看見了向陽莊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得這裡這麼近  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有考上的自信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃今天是一個人來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  今後我要獨自生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想第一天開始就要好好幹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要是不這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母都得一起跟過來  還要替我什麼都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就和至今沒有什麼區別了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在來這裡的途中  我一直在睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在電車裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是搬家卡車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是過於緊張的話  不知道為什麼就會困呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且連什麼時候睡著的也一點都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被搬家叔叔叫醒的時候  已經在向陽莊前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由也許是個大人物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那樣  只是睡著了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  一定是累壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,310)}{\bord0}怪人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經這個時候了  我要準備晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了這麼久真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係  要是還有想問的  要隨時來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我傷腦筋的時候  會隨時去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「天下無不散的宴席」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個一定要先拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這是新家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了  不過太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得  如果在這裡的話  能開心地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家裡沒有水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓～我～進～來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有點不安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\b1}{\fn細明體}「愛是盲目的」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才和我在一起的孩子  是新生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做由乃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天才剛搬過來  要好好幫助人家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很吵鬧  我猜到一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.24,0:21:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間是201？203？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,201  是美裡前輩住的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個個子小小的又可愛的孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,201嗎  要是沒有留下一些奇怪的機關就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  沙英  好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:21:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋  101室  二年級生\N賢妻良母·擅長做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英  102室  二年級生\N才色兼備·博學多識
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮子  202室  一年級生\N天真爛漫·單刀直入
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  201室  一年級生\N全家平安·拚命努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}結束  待續
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:25.96,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も知らない　世界が広がって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:25.96,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無人知曉的世界延展著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:31.93,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}繋がる　どこまでも　綴る糸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:31.93,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}到處連接著　相互縫合的線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.73,0:22:38.92,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}逆さまの世界　意外と楽しいんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.73,0:22:38.92,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}相反的世界　會意外的有趣吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:44.95,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}繋がる　どこまでも　続く糸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:44.95,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}到處連接著　延續不斷的線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:51.07,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何処かで今日も　君が笑っている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:51.07,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今天你也在某處歡笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:58.22,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ出逢える日まで　ずっと走る夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:58.22,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直到重逢為止　我一直奔跑的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:04.41,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}高鳴って流星レコード　君の歌声が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:04.41,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大聲作響的流星唱片  你的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:10.77,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕の胸を打つよ　流れ星の空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:10.77,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}叩擊著我的心　流星的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:17.23,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眩しい流星レコード　囁くその声が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:17.23,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}耀眼的流星唱片　低聲細語的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:23.71,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕を宇宙導く　流れ星の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:23.71,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}把我指引向宇宙　流星的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:30.26,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}聞こえない　届くかない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:30.26,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}能聽見　會傳達到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:35.46,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}探す　足跡を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:35.46,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}尋找足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.21,0:23:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  必須要去買豇豆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是覺得很不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.09,0:23:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豇豆和赤豆簡直一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼赤豆就不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤豆煮的話皮會破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說會聯繫到切腹  所以被討厭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.51,0:23:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.52,0:23:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是行走的百科全書
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.85,0:24:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  燒的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.38,0:24:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「2月6日  櫻花櫻花」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.62,0:24:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在向陽莊等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.12,0:24:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必要來看哦

